# textdomain: mcl_minecarts
Sneak-click to remove=潜行并点击来移除
Minecart=矿车
Vehicle for fast travel on rails=在铁轨上快速行驶的交通工具
Minecarts can be used for a quick transportion on rails.=矿车可用于在铁轨上快速运输。
Minecarts only ride on rails and always follow the tracks. At a T-junction with no straight way ahead, they turn left. The speed is affected by the rail type.=矿车只能在铁轨上行驶，并且始终沿着轨道行进。在前方没有直路的丁字路口处，它们会向左转弯。其速度受铁轨类型的影响。
You can place the minecart on rails. Right-click it to enter it. Punch it to get it moving.=你可以将矿车放置在铁轨上。右键点击它便可进入矿车。击打它就能让它动起来。
To obtain the minecart, punch it while holding down the sneak key.=若要获取矿车，在按住潜行键的同时击打即可。
If it moves over a powered activator rail, you'll get ejected.=如果它经过充能的激活铁轨，你就会被弹出。
Sneak to dismount=潜行以离开
Minecart with Chest=运输矿车
Minecart with Furnace=动力矿车
A minecart with furnace is a vehicle that travels on rails. It can propel itself with fuel.=带熔炉的矿车是一种在铁轨上行驶的交通工具。它可以用燃料来驱动自身。
Place it on rails. If you give it some coal, the furnace will start burning for a long time and the minecart will be able to move itself. Punch it to get it moving.=将它放置在铁轨上。如果你给它添加一些煤炭，熔炉就会长时间燃烧，矿车就能自行移动了。击打它可以让它动起来。
To obtain the minecart and furnace, punch them while holding down the sneak key.=若要获取带熔炉的矿车，在按住潜行键的同时击打它即可。
Minecart with Command Block=命令方块矿车
Minecart with Hopper=漏斗矿车
Minecart with TNT=炸药矿车
Can be ignited by tools or powered activator rail=可被工具点燃或通过充能的激活铁轨
A minecart with TNT is an explosive vehicle that travels on rail.=装有TNT的矿车是一种在铁轨上行驶的爆炸型交通工具。
Place it on rails. Punch it to move it. The TNT is ignited with a flint and steel or when the minecart is on an powered activator rail.=将它放置在铁轨上。击打它使其移动。可以用打火石和铁锭来点燃TNT，或者当矿车位于充能的激活铁轨上时，TNT也会被点燃。
To obtain the minecart and TNT, punch them while holding down the sneak key. You can't do this if the TNT was ignited.=若要获取装有TNT的矿车以及TNT，在按住潜行键的同时击打它们即可。但如果TNT已经被点燃了，就没办法这么做了。
Place them on the ground to build your railway, the rails will automatically connect to each other and will turn into curves, T-junctions, crossings and slopes as needed.=将它们放置在地面上以搭建你的铁路，铁轨会自动相互连接，并会根据需要变成弯道、丁字路口、交叉路口以及斜坡。
Rail=铁轨
Track for minecarts=矿车轨道
Rails can be used to build transport tracks for minecarts. Normal rails slightly slow down minecarts due to friction.=铁轨可用于为矿车建造运输轨道。普通铁轨由于存在摩擦力，会使矿车的速度稍有减慢。
Powered Rail=动力铁轨
Speed up when powered, slow down when not powered=通电时加速，不通电时减速
Rails can be used to build transport tracks for minecarts. Powered rails are able to accelerate and brake minecarts.=铁轨可用于为矿车建造运输轨道。充能铁轨能够使矿车加速和刹车。
Without redstone power, the rail will brake minecarts. To make this rail accelerate minecarts, power it with redstone power.=在没有红石能量时，这种铁轨会使矿车刹车。要让这种铁轨使矿车加速，需用红石能量为其充能。
Activator Rail=带激活器铁轨
Activates minecarts when powered=充能时可激活矿车
Rails can be used to build transport tracks for minecarts. Activator rails are used to activate special minecarts.=铁轨可用于为矿车建造运输轨道。激活铁轨用于激活特殊的矿车。
To make this rail activate minecarts, power it with redstone power and send a minecart over this piece of rail.=要让这种铁轨激活矿车，需用红石能量为其充能，然后让矿车经过这片铁轨。
Detector Rail=压敏铁轨
Emits redstone power when a minecart is detected=当检测到矿车时会发出红石能量
Rails can be used to build transport tracks for minecarts. A detector rail is able to detect a minecart above it and powers redstone mechanisms.=铁轨可用于为矿车建造运输轨道。探测铁轨能够探测到其上方的矿车，并为红石装置供能。
To detect a minecart and provide redstone power, connect it to redstone trails or redstone mechanisms and send any minecart over the rail.=要检测矿车并提供红石能量，将其与红石线路或红石装置相连，然后让任意矿车经过这条铁轨即可。
